    "This helps fill a critical gap in the literature on AI chatbots and their role in knowledge management, thus providing scholars with a new perspective to further explore.",
    "Secondly, the study highlighted the role of memorability in knowledge acquisition and application, another underexplored area in prior research.",
    "While existing literature has explored aspects of memorability in user interfaces and experiences 98, 99, few have delved into its role in AI chatbot contexts.",
    "The results demonstrate that ChatGPT's ability to remember user preferences and requirements significantly enhances knowledge acquisition and application, pointing to the importance of developing AI systems with high memorability.",
    "For researchers in the field, this study sets the foundation for a more detailed exploration of the significance of memorability as a crucial component of the user experience with AI systems."
